SimulationType                MonteCarlo
NumberOfCycles                600000
NumberOfInitializationCycles  600000
PrintEvery                    15000
PrintPropertiesEvery          15000
Forcefield                    local
ChargeMethod                  none
CutOffVDW                     {cutoff:.2f}
RestartFile                   no

Framework 0 
            FrameworkName                 simulation
            UnitCells                     {na:d} {nb:d} {nc:d}
            RemoveAtomNumberCodeFromLabel yes
	    ExternalTemperature           298
            ExternalPressure              10 
            Movies                        no
            WriteMoviesEvery              9000

Component 0 MoleculeName                  D4
            MoleculeDefinition            local
            TranslationProbability        0.5
            RotationProbability           0.5
            ReinsertionProbability        0.5
            CFSwapLambdaProbability       1.0
	    CreateNumberOfMolecules       0

